193
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,560
That's a real crane.

194
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,160
I thought it was...

195
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,160
That's real.

196
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,280
I thought it was a statue too.

197
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:46,960
A real crane.

198
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:47,520
Really.

199
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,880
So beautiful.

200
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:03,880
This is Teng's hometown.

201
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:05,520
