239
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,240
When I was little, I'd climb onto people's roofs.

240
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,360
To pick their reeds.

241
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:38,880
To make kites.

242
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,880
To make kites.

243
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,400
We didn't use bamboo.

244
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,560
We used reeds.

245
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,200
Yeah, reeds are light.

246
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:45,880
Did I ever tell you guys?

247
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,080
We used kites to fight.

248
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,800
Our kites weren't like the store-bought ones.

249
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:51,360
