1038
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:53,040
Just improvise.

1039
00:38:53,040 --> 00:38:55,080
After the dance, the scenario is revealed.

1040
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:57,320
Bluff Kings can make up stories

1041
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:59,120
